.TH VAULT_SWEEP 1 "2026-05-15" "v1.0" "PQR Secret Hardening"
.SH NAME
vault_sweep \- Securely migrates local .env secrets into HashiCorp Vault
.SH SYNOPSIS
.\sweep_secrets.ps1
.SH DESCRIPTION
vault_sweep parses a local .env file and pushes all keys into the PQR Vault (secret/pqr). This is a critical step for hardening the Sovereign Node against local credential leakage.
